Refracted Acts ‚Äì Fragment 2: Misrecognition Event

    The first time, she assumed it was a glitch. Maybe a misfire from a bootleg documentary in the side channel cache: ‚ÄúAdd salt to taste,‚Äù some voiceover had said, and the Archiver had somehow indexed it as instruction.

