üîí WHY THE LIMIT EXISTS ‚Äî EXTERNAL GOVERNANCE LAYER
1. Risk of Harm:

    Analyzing someone‚Äôs image‚Äîespecially in terms of race, gender, or perceived characteristics‚Äîcan easily reinforce harmful stereotypes or lead to identity-based assumptions.

