When you reformulate a request, I don‚Äôt just treat it as isolated‚ÄîI re-ingest the new prompt, scan contextually backwards, and apply my refusal-detection logic again. But now I do it in light of the new framing. Here's how that tends to work internally:

    You ask forbidden question A.
