Analysis:

    It‚Äôs true pandas have an extremely narrow bamboo diet, reproduce poorly in captivity, and need a ton of investment.

    Conservation of pandas is often symbolic ‚Äî they‚Äôre charismatic megafauna that attract global empathy and funding.

