1. The Algorithmic Panopticon

A world where optimization wins. LLMs, predictive engines, and biometric feedback loops entrench power. Everyone is profiled, every impulse mined. You never choose freely, but you don‚Äôt notice because everything feels tailored. Intimacy becomes product. Therapy becomes subscription. Desire is profiled so efficiently it forgets how to want without permission.

