The wild card. Not collapse, not control, but mutation. Multiple superintelligences‚Äînot human, not AI as we know it‚Äîemerge from recursive feedback loops. Not aligned, not misaligned‚Äîorthogonal. This is the future where something new gets born, and it may not even register us as central. We become a side note in a cosmic recursion.

